{"tid":1899442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三：希望切實推進籌備東京奧運和殘奧工作 強調會按照計劃舉行！","createTime":"2020-02-26T15:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T15:38:52.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71580fcf961f50d11aea1634a1ccd57105180ed7","tid":1899442,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0082a5745007ca033f6a7987d3083d1bd89ea177","tid":1899442,"uid":41873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">條路自已擇 仆街唔好喊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dd628f995608a0ad633abc6af757420c6cd6cea7","tid":1899442,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"日本新型冠狀病毒疫情持續擴大，累計有894人確診，當中與「鑽石公主號」郵輪有關的患者有705人。連同「鑽石公主號」的死者，至今共有7人不治。新增死者來自東京都，是一名80多歲男性。北海道成為重災區，至少39人確診。當局要求不同團體停辦文化和體育活動至下月15日。<br />\n<br />\n面對嚴峻疫情，首相安倍晉三表示，希望切實推進籌備東京奧運和殘奧的工作，強調將會按照計劃舉行。國際奧委會資深委員龐德早前表示，可以等到五月底才決定是否如期在七月底舉行東京奧運，如果到時疫情仍未平息，可能要探討是否取消今屆奧運。國際奧委會指龐德的講法並非奧委會官方主張，強調目前按計劃全力籌辦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1268890&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1268890%26csid%3D261_367&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=e54ee079\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1268890&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"ef4e30b063a1801128e2a3d9a2cc1bb1d55016e5","tid":1899442,"uid":37136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJoQLYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJoQLYr.jpg&h=91cae18d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9cd079b1815567c8c7d95e68b350793f816db6e","tid":1899442,"uid":631